videos.description: Travis Dye makes the easy grab on the pass from Anthony Brown to score an 11-yard Oregon touchdown.

videos.headline: Anthony Brown dives for the pylon for Oregon TD
videos.description: Anthony Brown evades defenders and dives for the pylon to score a 17-yard touchdown for Oregon to extend their lead to 24-14.

videos.headline: Byron Cardwell slips through the defense for 27-yard TD
